Package mars.util

Class GenMath

  • java.lang.Object
    • mars.util.GenMath

  • public class GenMath
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contain arithmetic functions for abstract numbers (i.e, 32/64 bit long number). Unfortunately, Java doesn't support operands overload, so this class was needed to make this abstraction. Note that each function's name is identical to its relative command in RISCV.
    Version:
    September 2019
    Author:
    Maya Peretz
